{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Quadphos</strong> is a grid-based rule deduction logic puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each puzzle consists of a grid and several numerical clues. Your goal is to light up the cells to satisfy all the numerical clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The symbols next to the numbers represent the specific rules that these clues follow. For example, a number might indicate the number of lit cells within its range.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game doesn't directly tell you these rules. You'll need to deduce and verify their meanings through a series of levels. As you solve puzzles, you'll continually refine your guesses, or even discard them entirely, until you discover a more exciting perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Once you grasp the new rules, you can tackle more complex puzzles and enjoy the challenge of combining multiple rules for a greater difficulty.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">20+ unique and engaging rules</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">600+ handcrafted puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each puzzle has a single solution</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439710/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738755179","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439710/page.bg.jpg?t=1738755179","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439710/24ecea102b793b2c405faf4474c8fb8cc0c34152/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738755179","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439710/24ecea102b793b2c405faf4474c8fb8cc0c34152/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738755179","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3487950,